hadiths[15]{hadithnumber,text}:
2375,Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unkey walid (Hazrat Bashir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) unhen uthaey huye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur arz kiya : gawah rahen ke mainey Noman ko apney maal mein sey falan falan chiz hiba (hadiya) kar di hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum ney apney sarey beton ko wesi chiz di hai jaisi Noman ko di hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to is (hiba) par merey siwa kisi aur ko gawah bana lo. phir farmaya : kya tumhen ye baat pasand nahin ke wo sab tum sey barabar husne-suluk karen? Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ji haan (pasand hai). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tab (is tarah) nahin (karna chahiye).
2376,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unkey walid ney unhen eik ghulam hiba (hadiya) kiya. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye taake aap ko is par gawah bana lein. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum ney apni tamam aulad ko yehi kuchh diya hai? unhoney kaha : ji nahin. aap ney farmaya, phir usey wapis ley lo."
2377,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi key liye jayez nahin ke (kisi ko) koi chiz dey kar wapis ley ley, siwaye walid key, jo kuchh wo apni aulad ko deta hai, (usey wapis ley sakta hai)."
2378,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey , wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs apney hiba sey ruju na karey magar walid apni aulad sey (wapis ley sakta hai)."
2379,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Umri kuchh nahin. jis ko umr bhar key liye koi chiz di gaee, wo usi ki ho gaee."
2380,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jisney kisi shakhs ko umra key taur par kuchh diya to wo us (wasul karney waley) ka aur uskey bachchon ka hai. umra karney waley ki baat sey is mein uska haq khatam ho gaya, wo chiz uski hai jisey umr bhar key liye di gaee, aur uski aulad key liye hai."
2381,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney umra ko waris key liye qarar diya.
2382,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raqbaa kuchh nahin, jisey raqbaa key tor par koi chiz di gaee , wo zindagi mein bhi aur marney par bhi usi ki hai.  Raavi ney bayan kya : raqbaa ka matlab doosrey sey ye kehna hai : ye chiz uski hai jo hum dono mein sey baad mein faut ho."
2383,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umra us shakhs key haq mein jari hoga jisey umraa key tor par diya gaya. aur raqbaa us shakhs key haq mein jari hoga jisey raqbaa key tor par diya gaya."
2384,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apna Atiya wapis leta hai, wo kuttey ki tarah hai, jo khata rehta hai, jab sair ho jata hai to qai kar deta hai, phir apni qai ko dobara khaney lag jata hai."
2385,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hiba kar key wapis leney wala apni qai ko wapis pet mein dalney waley ki tarah hai."
2386,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apna hiba wapis leney wala us kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai ko dobara khata hai."
2387,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi apney hiba (tohfey) ka ziyada haq rakhta hai, jab tak usey uska badla (jawabi tohfa) na diya jaey."
2388,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik khutba diya. is mein aap ney farmaya : aurat ko khawind ki ijazat key baghair apney maal mein tasarruf (dakhal) jayez nahin, jabke wo uski ismat ka Malik ho (jab tak nikah qaaim ho)."
2389,"Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad mein sey eik sahab Hazrat Abdullah bin Yahya (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke un ki daadi, yani Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Hazrat Khaira‬ (Raziallahu anha) apna zewar ley kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kiya : main ye sadqa karti hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat key liye khawind ki ijazat key baghair apney maal mein tasarruf (dakhal) karna durust nahin. kya tum ney Kaab sey ijazat li hai? unhoney kaha : haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey khawind Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas pegham bhej kar daryaft farmaya : kya tum ney Khaira ko ijazat di hai ke wo apna zewar sadqa kar dey? unhoney kaha : ji haan. chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey sadqa wasul farma liya."
